column2: Why do I feel like I know this house? None of this makes any sense.
Last time I was outside, but I couldn’t help but feel like those things were drawn to me. They completely ignored the nearby children.
There is no end to these things. The more I fight, the less I know about them. Where are they all coming from?
I’m having more and more dreams about this house. Could they be memories? I’ve definitely been here before.
Maybe I should research these things on the internet more. Somebody has to have seen something.
The dreams are getting more frequent. I was playing in a room I haven’t seen yet. I remember playing with my grandfather.
I think I saw a locked area. Maybe I can find my grandfather there. Maybe he can help me make sense of all of this.
